Text: Lifting the Rate Cap BriefAttached is a redline redraft of the Joint Initial Brief Opposing Limitations on Lifting the Rate Cap to Exclude Pipeline ShortTerm Service Please let me know if your company intends to be a petitioner or intervener in support on the brief Consistent with an email you will be receiving from Joan Dreskin please furnish any comments to me by Wednesday March and we will email a final draft to you by Tuesday March James D McKinney Jr RedlineBriefdoc
